headline: Eversource: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The results beat Wall Street expectations. The average estimate of five analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of $1.10 per share. The New England power provider posted revenue of $3.37 billion in the period, missing Street forecasts.

headline: Eversource Energy Reports Full-Year & Fourth Quarter 2025 Results
summary: HARTFORD, Conn. & BOSTON, February 12, 2026--Eversource Energy (NYSE: ES) today reported full-year 2025 earnings of $1.69 billion, or $4.56 per share, compared with full-year 2024 earnings of $811.7 million, or $2.27 per share.
